gn Stage**: ST-3 Completed\\n7: \\n8: ## Task Breakdown\\n9: \\n10: ### Task 1: Analyze existing build infrastructure\\n11: - [ ] Review root Makefile (if exists) at project root\\n12: - [ ] Review existing build scripts in ci-cd/ directory\\n13: - [ ] Review go.mod for Go module structure\\n14: - [ ] Review pyproject.toml for Python package structure\\n15: - [ ] Review cmd/ directory for all Go binaries\\n16: - [ ] Review agentcube/ directory for Python SDK structure\\n17: - [ ] Review existing AR-032 Makefile as reference for Docker builds\\n18: - [ ] Document current build commands and workflows\\n19: - [ ] Identify gaps in build automation\\n20: - [ ] List all binaries and packages that need build targets\\n21: \\n22: **Verification**: Comprehensive understanding of existing build infrastructure and requirements\\n23: \\n24: ---\\n25: \\n26: ### Task 2: Design root Makefile structure\\n27: - [ ] Define top-level variables (GO, GOFLAGS, GOBIN, etc.)\\n28: - [ ] Define Python-related variables (PYTHON, PIP, etc.)\\n29: - [ ] Define Docker-related variables (DOCKER, DOCKER_BUILDKIT, etc.)\\n30: - [ ] Define build directories (BUILD_DIR, DIST_DIR, etc.)\\n31: - [ ] Define version variables (VERSION, GIT_COMMIT, BUILD_TIME)\\n32: - [ ] ...\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884532447,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28508bd72ffeXIhFXu0VWKX43w\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af77aa6001F7yVSh2hL8LRG0\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7af76f42001JinHhD9e3AQiP3\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28508bd72ffeXIhFXu0VWKX43w\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-58120de969ec4304931934ccf3e019e0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: 为 AgentCube 项目在根目录创建统一的 Makefile 构建目标体系，提供标准化的构建、测试、清理、代码质量检查和容器镜像构建操作。该 Makefile 将整合 Go 二进制文件构建、Python 包管理、多语言测试、Docker 镜像构建以及开发工作流自动化，为开发者提供单一入口点来执行所有常见任务。\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: 实现统一的 Makefile 构建目标体系，达到以下目标：\\n10: \\n11: - **统一构建接口** - 提供单一入口点执行所有构建、测试、清理操作\\n12: - **多语言支持** - 同时支持 Go 和 Python 项目的构建和测试\\n13: - **开发效率提升** - 通过标准化的目标和别名简化常见操作\\n14: - **CI/CD 友好** - 目标命名和输出格式便于 CI/CD 管道集成\\n15: - **可扩展性** - 模块化设计便于添加新的构建目标和规则\\n16: - **一致性** - 确保所有团队成员使用相同的构建命令和参数\\n17: - **自文档化** - 通过 help 目标提供完整的使用说明\\n18: \\n19: ## Module\\n20: \\n21: `root` - 项目根目录\\n22: \\n23: ## Language\\n24: \\n25: Makefile (GNU Make 4.0+)\\n26: \\n27: ## Size\\n28: \\n29: M\\n30: \\n31: ## Scope\\n32: \\n33: ### In Scope\\n34: \\n35: 1. **Go 构建目标**\\n36:    - `build` - 构建所有 Go 二进制文件（agentd、picod、router、workload-manager）\\n37:    - `build-go` - Go 专用构建目标\\n38:    - `build-agentd` - 构建 agentd 二进制文件\\n39:    - `build-picod` - 构建 picod 二进制文件\\n40:    - `build-router` - 构建 router 二进制文件\\n41:    - `build-workloadmanager` - 构建 workload-manager 二进制文件\\n42:    - `build-cli` - 构建 CLI 工具\\n43: \\n44: 2. **Python 构建目标**\\n45:    - `build-python` - 构建 Python 包（wheel/sdist）\\n46:    - `install-python` - 安装 Python 依赖\\n47:    - `install-dev` - 安装开发依赖\\n48: \\n49: 3. **测试目标**\\n50:    - `test` - 运行所有测试（Go + Python）\\n51:    - `test-go` - ...\n  Line 23: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884539891,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28508bd72ffeXIhFXu0VWKX43w\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af79531001z7MFrVAlFiIXQ7\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7af77b0d001bcBhjhVXZIw6Gz\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28508bd72ffeXIhFXu0VWKX43w\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-58d4310c415645fe8fc4b53ac96c470b\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/delta-spec.md\",\"limit\":200},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencod