 ID is bootstrapped from Router or reused from existing session\\n8: - Context manager support ensures proper resource cleanup\\n9: - Invoke method handles HTTP communication via Router with proper timeout configuration\\n10: - Connection pooling is implemented via requests.Session\\n11: - Error handling includes session validation and HTTP error propagation\\n12: - Unit tests achieve >80% code coverage\\n13: - Integration tests work with real Router service\\n14: **Architecture:** Python SDK client with AgentRuntimeClient (main API) and AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient (HTTP layer), following context manager pattern for resource cleanup.\\n15: **Tech Stack:** Python 3.10+, requests ^2.31.0\\n16: **Frontend validation:** No\\n17: \\n18: ---\\n19: \\n20: ### Task 1: Verify AgentRuntimeClient class structure\\n21: \\n22: **Files:**\\n23: - Verify: `agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\\n24: - Verify: `agentcube/__init__.py`\\n25: \\n26: **Step 1: Write the failing test**\\n27: \\n28: ``...\n  Line 42: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884320169,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850cab71ffe5dB8FyygvpNmyl\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af42ff3001PWHSvI6xf5UA0L\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7af407c9001iJT3G7IMDSuwdf\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850cab71ffe5dB8FyygvpNmyl\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-40643a28ee7c4e0db3e079fc2b45e0b0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/Makefile\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/Makefile</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Makefile for AR-032 Dockerfile Multi-Stage Build\\n2: \\n3: .PHONY: help build build-all build-multiarch validate validate-build validate-runtime test clean\\n4: \\n5: # Default target\\n6: .DEFAULT_GOAL := help\\n7: \\n8: # Variables\\n9: GO_VERSION ?= 1.21\\n10: BUILD_VERSION ?= dev\\n