n32: - **GIVEN** a nil config is passed to `NewRouter`\\n33: - **WHEN** `NewRouter(config)` is called\\n34: - **THEN** a Router instance is returned with default configuration values\\n35: - **AND** default listen address is \\\":8080\\\"\\n36: - **AND** backend timeout is 30 seconds\\n37: - **AND** rate limiting is disabled by default\\n38: \\n39: #### Scenario: AR-039-001-B — Router creates with custom config\\n40: \\n41: - **GIVE...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-036_ST-7.log:\n  Line 17: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884307511,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850ecd5cffeWSGG7Qv6ca85DB\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af406b10016aC5HJeaCpWhIL\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7af3feb1001uLp2hvqXYSOeoy\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850ecd5cffeWSGG7Qv6ca85DB\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_9566c3ba23a3439fada9a8df\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-036_ST-6.log\",\"limit\":100},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-036_ST-6.log</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: EXIT_CODE: 0\\n2: STDOUT:\\n3: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"step_start\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1775883805052,\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_28513a79cffeGKOj7slrX3J3hz\\\",\\\"part\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"prt_d7aec6178001u0ZhY0xoLzcwO4\\\",\\\"messageID\\\":\\\"msg_d7aec5954001BSp6cUe4Q1ELEL\\\",\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_28513a79cffeGKOj7slrX3J3hz\\\",\\\"snapshot\\\":\\\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"step-start\\\"}}\\n4: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool_use\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1775883896844,\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_28513a79cffeGKOj7slrX3J3hz\\\",\\\"part\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"prt_d7aec6412001No1MW6cThH66qL\\\",\\\"messageID\\\":\\\"msg_d7aec5954001BSp6cUe4Q1ELEL\\\",\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_28513a79cffeGKOj7slrX3J3hz\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool\\\",\\\"tool\\\":\\\"task\\\",\\\"callID\\\":\\\"call_9469e3d3b12845678a84e442\\\",\\\"state\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\",\\\"input\\\":{\\\"description\\\":\\\"Explore agentcube project structure\\\",\\\"prompt\\\":\\\"Explore the directory /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z to find the agentcube project. Look for:\\\\n1. The integrations module/directory\\\\n2. Any dify-plugin related files (main.py, manifest.yaml, provider/, tools/, requirements.txt, etc.)\\\\n3. Test files related to the dify plugin integration\\\\n4. Any spec or design documents\\\\n\\\\nReturn the full directory structure of the integrations module and list all relevant files with their paths.\\\",\\\"subagent_type\\\":\\\"explore\\\"},\\\"output\\\"...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-034_ST-7.log:\n  Line 17: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884293681,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850c860affeZNdDKKGycv8yCT\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af3cb12001g0rhAwQRYVUmHP\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7af3c2a40015J8ttPjrshjaSu\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850c860affeZNdDKKGycv8yCT\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_cdb17e9b3917464989dea214\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-034/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-034/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-034: CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 GitHub Actions CI/CD 流水线体系，为代码质量、构建验证、镜像发布、安全扫描提供自动化流水线。该 CI/CD 体系是 AgentCube 工程化实践的核心基础设施，支撑持续集成、持续交付、质量门禁全流程。\\n6: \\n7: 目标是：\\n8: \\n9: 1. **代码质量门禁** - 在 PR 和 push 事件中自动运行 lint、typecheck、test，确保代码质量\\n10: 2. **构建验证** - 验证 Go 和 Python 代码可编译，Docker 镜像可构建\\n11: 3. **多架构支持** - 构建 amd64、arm64 多架构 Docker 镜像，支持异构集群\\n12: 4. **镜像发布** - 自动推送镜像到 GHCR，支持版本标签管理（latest, commit-sha, semver）\\n13: 5. **安全扫描** - 集成 Trivy 扫描镜像漏洞，集成 CodeQL 扫描代码安全问题\\n14: 6. **文档站点** - 自动构建和部署 Docusaurus 文档到 GitHub Pages\\n15: 7. **发布自动化** - 创建 GitHub Release，生成变更日志，上传构建产物\\n16: 8. **依赖更新** - 自动检测依赖更新，创建 Dependabot PR\\n17: \\n18: 本提案基于 AR-032（Dockerfile 多阶段构建）、AR-033（Makefile 构建目标）实现，遵循 GitHub Actions 最佳实践和 AgentCube 工程规范。\\n19: \\n20: ## Scope\\n21: \\n22: **Module:** .github  \\n23: **Language:** YAML  \\n24: **Size:** L\\n25: \\n26: 本 AR 包含：\\n27: \\n28: - **包含内容：**\\n29:   - `.github/workflows/ci.yml` - CI 流水线（lint, test, build）\\n30:   - `.github/workflows/cd.yml` - CD 流水线（镜像推送、发布）\\n31:   - `.github/workflows/security-scan.yml` - 安全扫描（Trivy, CodeQL）\\n32:   - `.github/workflows/docs.yml` - 文档构建和部署\\n33:   - `.github/workflows/multi-arch-build.yml` - 多架构镜像构建\\n34:   - `.github/workflows/e2e-test.yml` - 端到端测试\\n35:   - `.github/workflows/nightly-build.yml` - 夜间构建\\n36:   - `.github/wor...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-033_ST-3.log:\n  Line 14: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884152378,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850e73e3ffeAvVnlVddEs8ZEm\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af1a8420012SacoSSEclQ1S5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7af19e19001id0CFoyC3tekKl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850e73e3ffeAvVnlVddEs8ZEm\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-45336740b646476cbb59a5d820860c25\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/Makefile\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/Makefile</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Makefile for AR-032 Dockerfile Multi-Stage Build\\n2: \\n3: .PHONY: help build build-all build-multiarch validate validate-build validate-runtime test clean\\n4: \\n5: # Default target\\n6: .DEFAULT_GOAL := help\\n7: \\n8: # Variables\\n9: GO_VERSION ?= 1.21\\n10: BUILD_VERSION ?= dev\\n11: BUILD_TIME ?= $(shell date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ)\\n12: GIT_COMMIT ?= $(shell git rev-parse --short HEAD 2>/dev/null || echo 'unknown')\\n13: IMAGE_NAME ?= agentcube\\n14: TAG ?= latest\\n15: REGISTRY ?=\\n16: PLATFORMS ?= linux/amd64,linux/arm64\\n17: \\n18: # Colors\\n19: BLUE := \\\\033[0;34m\\n20: GREEN := \\\\033[0;32m\\n21: YELLOW := \\\\033[1;33m\\n22: NC := \\\\033[0m\\n23: \\n24: help: ## Show this help message\\n25: \\t@echo \\\"$(BLUE)AgentCube Docker Multi-Stage Build$(NC)\\\"\\n26: \\t@echo \\\"\\\"\\n27: \\t@echo \\\"$(GREEN)Usage:$(NC)\\\"\\n28: \\t@echo \\\"  make [target]\\\"\\n29: \\t@echo \\\"\\\"\\n30: \\t@echo \\\"$(GREEN)Targets:$(NC)\\\"\\n31: \\t@awk 'BEGIN {FS = \\\":.*?## \\\"} /^[a-zA-Z_-]+:.*?## / {printf \\\"  $(YELLOW)%-15s$(NC) %s\\\\n\\\", $$1, $$2}' $(MAKEFILE_LIST)\\n32: \\t@echo \\\"\\\"\\n33: \\t@echo \\\"$(GREEN)Variables:$(NC)\\\"\\n34: \\t@echo \\\"  GO_VERSION      Go version (default: $(GO_VERSION))\\\"\\n35: \\t@echo \\\"  BUILD_VERSION   Build version (default: $(BUILD_VERSION))\\\"\\n36: \\t@echo \\\"  BUILD_TIME      Build timestamp (default: $(BUILD_TIME))\\\"\\n37: \\t@echo \\\"  GIT_COMMIT      Git...\n  Line 24: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884164884,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850e73e3ffeAvVnlVddEs8ZEm\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af1dede0014frAHGVt8XEJiH\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7af1c7020018sIdwbf45Gtfy8\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850e73e3ffeAvVnlVddEs8ZEm\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-8fa29c669c37416c94613d09a929b485\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/build.sh\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-032/build.sh</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: #!/bin/bash\\n2: # Build script for AgentCube Docker images\\n3: \\n4: set -e\\n5: \\n6: # Default values\\n7: GO_VERSION=\\\"${GO_VERSION:-1.21}\\\"\\n8: BUILD_VERSION=\\\"${BUILD_VERSION:-dev}\\\"\\n9: BUILD_TIME=\\\"${BUILD_TIME:-$(date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ)}\\\"\\n10: GIT_COMMIT=\\\"${GIT_COMMIT:-$(git rev-parse --short HEAD 2>/dev/null || echo 'unknown')}\\\"\\n11: IMAGE_NAME=\\\"${IMAGE_NAME:-agentcube}\\\"\\n12: REGISTRY=\\\"${REGISTRY:-}\\\"\\n13: \\n14: # Colors for output\\n15: RED='\\\\033[0;31m'\\n16: GREEN='\\\\033[0;32m'\\n17: YELLOW='\\\\033[1;33m'\\n18: NC='\\\\033[0m' # No Color\\n19: \\n20: log_info() {\\n21:     echo -e \\\"${GREEN}[INFO]${NC} $1\\\"\\n22: }\\n23: \\n24: log_warn() {\\n25:     echo -e \\\"${YELLOW}[WARN]${NC} $1\\\"\\n26: }\\n27: \\n28: log_error() {\\n29:     echo -e \\\"${RED}[ERROR]${NC} $1\\\"\\n30: }\\n31: \\n32: # Parse command line arguments\\n33: TARGET=\\\"${1:-runtime}\\\"\\n34: shift || true\\n35: \\n36: while [[ $# -gt 0 ]]; do\\n37:     case $1 in\\n38:         -t|--tag)\\n39:             TAG=\\\"$2\\\"\\n40:             shift 2\\n41:             ;;\\n42:         -p|--push)\\n43:             PUSH=true\\n44:             shift\\n45:             ;;\\n46:         --platform)\\n47:             PLATFORM=\\\"$2\\\"\\n48:             shift 2\\n49:             ;;\\n50:         -h|--help)\\n51:             echo \\\"Usage: $0 [TARGET] [OPTIONS]\\\"\\n52:             echo \\\"\\\"\\n53:             ...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z_logs/AR-019_ST-6.log:\n  Line 34: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884003390,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28511ffceffewS2lk4UDYNlI7A\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aef676b001A6SLv60c1tuPj9\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aef3cac001eEYaREPcvuNzyq\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28511ffceffewS2lk4UDYNlI7A\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"skill\",\"callID\":\"toolu_functions.skill:14\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"name\":\"quality-gate\"},\"output\":\"<skill_content name=\\\"quality-gate\\\">\\n# Skill: quality-gate\\n\\n> **SOP 位置**: 本 skill 是 `docs/SOP.md` Step 2 的执行细节。\\n> **上一步**: 代码开发 (Step 1) | **下一步**: `request-review` (Step 3a)\\n\\n# Quality Gate\\n\\n开发完成到提 review 之间的双重关卡：对照 spec 自检 + 用真实命令输出证明你的声明。\\n\\n## 核心知识\\n\\n**两条铁律合一**：\\n\\n1. **Spec alignment**（来自 `spec-compliance-check`）：AC 可能写偏，先回读原始需求，再逐项验收\\n2. **Evidence before claims**（来自 `verification-before-completion`）：没有运行命令、没看到输出，就不能说\\\"通过了\\\"\\n\\n> 铁律：`NO COMPLETION CLAIMS WITHOUT FRESH VERIFICATION EVIDENCE`\\n>\\n> 自问：\\\"我是这次真的运行了命令并看到输出，还是我只是相信它能工作？\\\"\\n\\n**为什么 AC 可能不够**：AC 是人写的，可能遗漏 UX 要求或场景覆盖。F041 教训：AC 全打勾，但铲屎官的原始需求（能力显示描述、多项目管理）根本没进 AC——spec compliance check 检查了 AC，但 AC 本身就是错的。\\n\\n## 流程\\n\\n```\\nBEFORE 声称完成 / 提 review:\\n\\nStep 0: VISION CHECK（愿景核对）\\n  ① 找原始 Discussion/Interview 文档（铲屎官原话在里面）\\n  ② 读核心痛点：\\\"我要...\\\"、\\\"我不想...\\\"\\n  ③ 问自己：铲屎官坐在 Hub 前用这个功能，体验是什么样的？\\n  ④ AC 是否完整覆盖了铲屎官的原始需求？\\n     → 如有遗漏，先补 AC 再继续\\n\\nStep 0.5: DELIVERY COMPLETENESS CHECK\\n  ① 这次交付的是完整 feat 还是 feat 的一部分？\\n     → 完整 feat：继续\\n     → 部分：有铲屎官明确同意分批交付的记录吗？没有就继续做完\\n  ② 本次产出后续需要\\\"重写\\\"还是\\\"扩展\\\"？\\n     → 扩展：通过\\n     → 重写：如果是已标注 Spike 且有结论，通过；否则不通过，回去重做\\n\\nStep 1: FIND — 找 spec/plan 文档\\n  - the active feature spec or implementation plan\\n  - 同时找 Discussion/Interview（铲屎官原话所在）\\n\\nStep 2: CREATE — 建检查清单\\n  - 列出每一个 AC / 功能点 / 边界条件\\n  - 列出 Discussion 里的 UX 描述和场景\\n\\nStep 3: VERIFY — 逐项检查\\n  - 代码在哪？有测试覆盖？边界处理了？\\n  - 🔴 交付物必须核实 commit/PR 状态（git log --grep + gh pr list）\\n    spec checkbox 是记录工具，不是真相源（LL-029）\\n  - 🔴 新增 MCP 工具 → `MCP_TOOLS_SECTION` 更新了吗？（F086 教训：造了工具猫不知道）\\n  - 🔴 新增行为规则 → governance digest / shared-rules 注入更新了吗？\\n\\nStep 4: RUNTIME GUARD — 前端证据...\n  Line 42: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884056400,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28511ffceffewS2lk4UDYNlI7A\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af0335b001UoKAuRqPUt8mOH\",\"messageID\":\"ms