le**: Makefile 构建目标体系\\n- **Module**: root\\n- **Language**: Makefile\\n- **Size**: M\\n- **Status**: Not Started\\n\\n## Description\\n\\nMakefile 构建目标体系，用于统一管理项目的构建、测试、清理等操作。\\n\\n## Dependencies\\n\\n- Go toolchain\\n- Python 3.11+\\n- Docker (for container builds)\\n\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[]},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/CHANGE.md\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775883986445,\"end\":1775883986461}}}}\n  Line 25: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775883986468,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285115a2effeS82cuMfDq5cS4K\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aef25f4001dUgw7MNzpP6gme\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aef0926001WqA6M3mL3X38TJ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285115a2effeS82cuMfDq5cS4K\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-ae5ee4ce37ad499bae5ebd248655a420\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: 为 AgentCube 项目在根目录创建统一的 Makefile 构建目标体系，提供标准化的构建、测试、清理、代码质量检查和容器镜像构建操作。该 Makefile 将整合 Go 二进制文件构建、Python 包管理、多语言测试、Docker 镜像构建以及开发工作流自动化，为开发者提供单一入口点来执行所有常见任务。\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: 实现统一的 Makefile 构建目标体系，达到以下目标：\\n10: \\n11: - **统一构建接口** - 提供单一入口点执行所有构建、测试、清理操作\\n12: - **多语言支持** - 同时支持 Go 和 Python 项目的构建和测试\\n13: - **开发效率提升** - 通过标准化的目标和别名简化常见操作\\n14: - **CI/CD 友好** - 目标命名和输出格式便于 CI/CD 管道集成\\n15: - **可扩展性** - 模块化设计便于添加新的构建目标和规则\\n16: - **一致性** - 确保所有团队成员使用相同的构建命令和参数\\n17: - **自文档化** - 通过 help 目标提供完整的使用说明\\n18: \\n19: ## Module\\n20: \\n21: `root` - 项目根目录\\n22: \\n23: ## Language\\n24: \\n25: Makefile (GNU Make 4.0+)\\n26: \\n27: ## Size\\n28: \\n29: M\\n30: \\n31: ## Scope\\n32: \\n33: ### In Scope\\n34: \\n35: 1. **Go 构建目标**\\n36:    - `build` - 构建所有 Go 二进制文件（agentd、picod、router、workload-manager）\\n37:    - `build-go` - Go 专用构建目标\\n38:    - `build-agentd` - 构建 agentd 二进制文件\\n39:    - `build-picod` - 构建 picod 二进制文件\\n40:    - `build-router` - 构建 router 二进制文件\\n41:    - `build-workloadmanager` - 构建 workload-manager 二进制文件\\n42:    - `build-cli` - 构建 CLI 工具\\n43: \\n44: 2. **Python 构建目标**\\n45:    - `build-python` - 构建 Python 包（wheel/sdist）\\n46:    - `install-python` - 安装 Python 依赖\\n47:    - `install-dev` - 安装开发依赖\\n48: \\n49: 3. **测试目标**\\n50:    - `test` - 运行所有测试（Go + Python）\\n51:    - `test-go` - ...\n  Line 36: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1775884003345,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285115a2effeS82cuMfDq5cS4K\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aef680d001R9y1UFUsdq7B1N\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aef63cf001uuMhGKXeMxo1f1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285115a2effeS82cuMfDq5cS4K\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n  Line 40: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884136163,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285115a2effeS82cuMfDq5cS4K\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af16e70001gukY1aDIw2lW5V\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aef6b88001m9tUtTXK1qOuQX\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285115a2effeS82cuMfDq5cS4K\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-f9af1642e3f142af98972ff34741bfb6\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-033 — Makefile 构建目标体系 Delta Specification\\n\\n## AR Metadata\\n- **AR ID**: AR-033\\n- **Title**: Makefile 构建目标体系\\n- **Module**: root\\n- **Language**: Makefile\\n- **Size**: M\\n- **Status**: Implementation Required\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\nThis delta specification provides comprehensive acceptance criteria for the Makefile build target system in the AgentCube project. It defines requirements for a unified build system that manages building, testing, cleaning, code quality checks, and Docker image builds for both Go and Python components. The specification ensures a standardized, efficient, and developer-friendly build interface with detailed GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios to verify proper implementation of all build targets and features.\\n\\n## Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Makefile structure and organization\\n\\nThe system SHALL implement a modular Makefile structure with a main Makefile in the root directory and organized sub-Makefiles for different language and functional areas.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Root Makefile exists and is properly structured\\n- **GIVEN** the AgentCube project root directory\\n- **WHEN** examining the directory structure\\n- **THEN** a Makefile SHALL exist in the root directory\\n- **AND** the Makefile SHALL be the main entry point for all build operations\\n- **AND** the Makefile SHALL include sub-Makefiles from .makefiles/ directory\\n\\n#### Scenario: .makefiles/ directory exists with sub-Makefiles\\n- **GIVEN** the .makefiles/ directory\\n- **WHEN** examining its contents\\n- **THEN** go.mk SHALL exist for Go-specific build rules\\n- **AND** python.mk SHALL exist for Python-specific build rules\\n- **AND** doc...\n  Line 43: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775884141412,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285115a2effeS82cuMfDq5cS4K\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af1764e001CxywlW0lLzJ6Nr\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7af16f1a001cLnGSHG2sX1d1w\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285115a2effeS82cuMfDq5cS4K\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've created `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/delta-spec.md` with comprehensive OpenSpec format acceptance criteria covering:\\n\\n**12 major requirement sections with 90+ GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios:**\\n- Makefile structure and organization\\n- Go build targets (agentd, picod, CLI, cross-platform)\\n- Python build targets (wheel, dependencies, virtual env)\\n- Test targets (unit, integration, coverage, race detection)\\n- Code quality targets (lint, format, check)\\n- Clean targets (build artifacts, Docker resources)\\n- Docker build targets (multi-stage, push, multi-arch)\\n- Development tool targets (dev up/down, watch, run)\\n- Documentation targets (generate, serve, build)\\n- Dependency management (download, update, verify)\\n- Version and release targets\\n- Help and metadata targets\\n\\n**Plus sections on:**\\n- Backward compatibility\\n- Dependencies (GNU Make 4.0+, Go 1.24+, Python 3.11+, Docker 20.10+)\\n- Security considerations (dependency verification, minimal attack surface)\\n- Comprehensive testing strategy\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775884141410,\"end\":1775884141410}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-036_ST-6.log:\n  Line 44: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775883969209,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28513a79cffeGKOj7slrX3J3hz\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aeea3da001c1K1MyTyG033nW\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aee7b63001v4tkHoltinsBre\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28513a79cffeGKOj7slrX3J3hz\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The directory name `dify-plugin` has a hyphen which is invalid for Python module imports. I need to fix the test imports:\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775883969208,\"end\":1775883969208}}}\n  Line 52: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1775883994368,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28513a79cffeGKOj7slrX3J3hz\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aef44ea001aYTVIwTC4yG0jM\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aef355c001uGDJiGsUzVGjYl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28513a79cffeGKOj7slrX3J3hz\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":36941,\"input\":36840,\"output\":54,\"reasoning\":47,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0.010334591}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-034_ST-5.log:\n  Line 35: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775883733308,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28516c8a4ffeyklEf33zHwrJZe\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aeae88f00174PeOWWp7jXRSe\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ae9ce820014rWhlfmbfgT7d2\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28516c8a4ffeyklEf33zHwrJZe\",\"type\